PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776885106
OL,3,CHalf of young Brits say they would
OL,4,Cnever fight for their country
OL,6,FSome respondents reported feeling
OL,7,Fworried by global conflicts happening
OL,8,Fin Gaza and Ukraine, but they were not
OL,9,Ffound to be a priority concern of
OL,10,Fyoung people.
OL,12,FInstead, 16 to 29-year-olds said the
OL,13,Ftop issues facing the country were the
OL,14,Fcost of living, affordability of
OL,15,Fhousing, healthcare, immigration and
OL,16,Fjob security - in particular, the fear
OL,17,Fthat AI could replace jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
