OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776885106
OL,3,CHalf of young Brits say they would
OL,4,Cnever fight for their country
OL,6,FThe government has described a
OL,7,F"recruitment and retention crisis" in
OL,8,Fthe Armed Forces, referring to a
OL,9,Fpersistent decline in the number of UK
OL,10,FRegulars and Reservists.
OL,12,FThe government says it currently has
OL,13,Fno plans to introduce mandatory
OL,14,Fnational service, but has proposed
OL,15,Fmilitary gap years for school leavers
OL,16,Fto get more young people interested in
OL,17,FArmed Forces careers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
